      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……うふふ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe…uhu…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん？\nやけに楽しそうですけど何かあったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san?\nYou seem unusually happy. Did something happen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "実はね、今から新しい衣装の試着をしに行くのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ you know‚ I'm going to try on a new outfit now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "新しい衣装ってわくわくするわよね\n今度はどんなデザインなのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Trying on new outfits is so exciting‚ you know.\nI wonder what kind of design it is this time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば今回の衣装制作は橋本さんに一任したから\n俺もまだ詳しくは聞けてなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ I left the outfit production entirely to Hashimoto-san this time.\nI haven't had a chance to ask for details yet…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "さとみちゃんからは「あの衣装を遙子さんが着れば\n注目を集めること間違いなしです！」って言われたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Satomi-chan told me‚\n\"If you wear that outfit‚ Haruko-san‚ it's sure to attract attention!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "新しい衣装で私の地味なイメージを\n一掃しちゃうんだから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With this new outfit‚\nI'll completely sweep away my plain image!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.7,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}